# bookfellow-www write scope

You are in the **Bookfellow product/www** silo (`bookfellow-www/`).

## Allowed writes

- Paths under this silo root (`bookfellow-www/`)
- **Carve-out:** TrueNAS app **`bookfellow` only** — hub paths needed to maintain it:
